Statistic Name Descriptions

  • Watershed area (km2) - The area of the watershed (km2).
  • Riparian buffer area (km2) - The area of the riparian buffer.
  • Vegetation area (km2) - The area of the riparian buffer classified as vegetation.
  • Not-vegetation area (km2) - The area of the riparian buffer classified as not-vegetation
  • Vegetation coverage (%) - The percentage of the riparian buffer's area that is covered by vegetation
  • Not-vegetation coverage (%) - The percentage of the riparian buffer's area that is not covered by vegetation
  • Mean area of not-vegetation patches (km2) - The mean area (km2) of the not-vegetation features in the riparian buffer
  • Number of riparian buffer features - The number of separate riparian buffer features
  • Number of vegetation features - The number of separate vegetation features in the riparian buffer
  • Number of not-vegetation features - The number of separate not-vegetation features in the riparian buffer
  • Perimeter of riparian buffer (km) - The total perimeter (km) of the riparian buffer features.
  • Perimeter of riparian buffer (km) - The total perimeter (km) of the riparian buffer features.
  • Perimeter of not-vegetation features (km) - The total perimeter of not-vegetation features.
  • Vegetation Connectivity - The quotient of the number of riparian buffer features divided by the number of vegetation features.
  • Vegetation Compactness - The normalized isoperimetric ratio (see README.md for more info)
